org.rdkit.knime.nodes.mcs

Class RDKitMCSNodeDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • DefaultNodeSettingsPane
      • org.rdkit.knime.nodes.mcs.RDKitMCSNodeDialog

  • public class RDKitMCSNodeDialog
extends DefaultNodeSettingsPane
    NodeDialog for the "RDKit MCS" Node. This node dialog derives from DefaultNodeSettingsPane which allows creation of a simple dialog with standard components. If you need a more complex dialog please derive directly from org.knime.core.node.NodeDialogPane.
    Author:
    Manuel Schwarze
